#### use qsurv to generate quantiles for weibull distribution
H1 = function(x) x^3
qsurv(seq(0.1, 0.9, 0.2), H0 = H1) ### shall be the same as
qweibull(seq(0.1, 0.9, 0.2), 3)
#### to get random survival time from the cumulative hazard function H1(t)
rsurv(15, H0 = H1)
}
